channel.title: Dump beta NPC list
channel.description: Hello. I'm trying to dump an NPC list (with combat levels) from the Evolution of Combat beta cache, but I've no idea how I would do that. Is there a specific program that can dump an NPC list from a given cache? If it's more complicated, would someone be willing to help me with it (or if I'm lucky enough, do it for me)? Thanks!
